---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Indian Catering Vancouver | Wedding & Corporate Catering | Sula Since 2010"
	description="Award-winning Indian catering Vancouver since 2010. Wedding catering, corporate catering, samosa & finger food catering across Vancouver, Burnaby, Richmond and Surrey."
	canonical="/"
>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/vancouver-catering-weddings.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>The Art of <em>Indian Catering</em><br/>in Vancouver</h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">From small dinners to big weddings. Real food, beautifully presented, with 15 years behind every plate.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Begin Your Event</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Vancouver's Most Trusted <em>Indian Catering</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>For over fifteen years, Sula has catered Vancouver's finest occasions. If you're planning <a href="/weddings" class="body-link">wedding catering</a>, an office lunch, or a Diwali celebration, our kitchen brings the same care to every plate. We serve <a href="/catering-vancouver" class="body-link">catering across Vancouver</a>, <a href="/catering-burnaby" class="body-link">Burnaby</a>, <a href="/catering-richmond" class="body-link">Richmond</a>, and <a href="/catering-surrey" class="body-link">Surrey</a>. Our menus draw from North Indian, South Indian, Hyderabadi, and Goan traditions, with house-ground spices, halal-certified meats, and vegan and gluten-friendly options on every menu.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-office.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver Burnaby Richmond" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Our Catering Services</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Catering for Every <em>Occasion</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal" aria-label="Wedding catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-wedding-catering.webp" alt="Indian wedding catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Most Loved</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Sangeet, ceremony, reception. Custom menus built with our chefs. Halal, vegetarian, vegan, Jain.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100" aria-label="Corporate catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/catering-services-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Corporate catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Trusted by Vancouver's Best</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Boardroom lunches, conferences, client entertaining. Hot delivery, on time, every time.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200" aria-label="Private party catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp" alt="Private party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Birthdays & Milestones</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, Diwali. Big feasts, easy delivery.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300" aria-label="Café and chai catering services">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Sula Cafe chai catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">From Sula Café</span>
							<h3>Café & <em>Chai</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai stations, specialty coffee bars, fresh-baked Indian pastries.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/wedding-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Sula wedding catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>Made with <em>Care.</em><br/>Served with <em>Soul.</em></h2>
					<p>Every menu starts with a conversation. We listen to your story, your guests, and your vision for the day. Then we build something that's exclusively yours, drawing from the regional cuisines of India and fifteen years catering Vancouver's finest occasions.</p>
					<p>We're proud to be part of the <a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="body-link">Sula Indian Restaurant</a> family, with four locations across Vancouver including our newest, <a href="https://sulacafe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="body-link">Sula Café</a> in East Van.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">15+</div><div class="stat-label">Years</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">2,000+</div><div class="stat-label">Events</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">4</div><div class="stat-label">Locations</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Authentic Flavours, <em>Easy Service</em></h2>
			<p>From boardroom to ballroom. We handle every detail.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Recent Events</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Moments <em>Worth Celebrating</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;font-size:16px;color:rgba(26,26,26,0.75)">A glimpse from our <a href="/gallery" class="body-link">full catering gallery</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="gallery-grid">
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale"><img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Indian food catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-100"><img src="/uploads/catering-near-me-vancouver-food-parties.webp" alt="Indian catering near me Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-200"><img src="/uploads/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Office catering Vancouver BC" loading="lazy" /></div>
				<div class="gallery-item reveal-scale delay-300"><img src="/uploads/birthday-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="Birthday party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top:60px">
				<a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline-dark">View Full Gallery</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark pattern-damask">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">Sula didn't just cater our wedding, they made it unforgettable. Every guest still talks about the food, and our coordinator made the entire day feel easy.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">Priya & Arjun · Wedding for 350 Guests</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">From the Journal</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Catering <em>Insights & Guides</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="related-links">
				<a href="/blog/indian-wedding-catering-vancouver-guide" class="related-link reveal">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/indian-wedding-catering.webp" alt="" /></div>

					<p class="meta">Wedding Planning · 8 min</p>
					<h4>Indian Wedding Catering: <em>The Complete Guide</em></h4>
					<p>Sangeet menus, halal certification, dietary planning, and everything we wish every couple knew before booking.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read the Guide →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/office-catering-vancouver-large-groups" class="related-link reveal delay-100">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-vancouver-corporate.webp" alt="" /></div>
					<p class="meta">Corporate Catering · 6 min</p>
					<h4>Office Catering: <em>Feeding 50+ at Work</em></h4>
					<p>Practical guidance on planning a large office lunch, including guest count, dietary needs, and delivery timing.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read More →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/halal-indian-catering-vancouver" class="related-link reveal delay-200">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/best-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="" /></div>

					<p class="meta">Catering Essentials · 5 min</p>
					<h4>Halal Indian <em>Catering</em></h4>
					<p>What halal certification actually means, how to ask the right questions, and why it matters for multi-cultural events.</p>
					<span class="arrow">Read More →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center reveal" style="margin-top:60px">
				<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-outline-dark">View All Articles</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Let's Plan Something <em>Beautiful</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
